$. The system is modeled by utilizing the random-walk theory and closely-related asymptotic results of the renewal theory, such as the inspection paradox and the Lorden&apos;s inequality. A~stability analysis is performed based on the regenerative approach. Some numerical results are included as well, showing that the obtained conditions delimit the stability region with high accuracy.}
